## Setup Scripts

☐ Add a script to init PYTHON & PIP to be able to use the CLI app
☐ Add a CLI app in front of the scripts
☐ Add the packages names to YML/JSON/other files
    ☐ Ex : xserver_pkg.yml, base_pkg.yml (git, vim, python2/3, cmake, zsh/fish, ranger, openssh)
☐ Add options to install all (like the current SETUP_ARCH.sh)
☐ Add options to install 1 by 1
    ☐ Add requirements for scripts ex: `lightdm` setup requires `xserver` setup

## Scripts

☐ Setup arch
☐ Setup xserver
☐ Setup Bumblebee
☐ Setup base AUR packages
